Aquí.

00:05:06.790 --> 00:05:07.300
¿Sí?

00:05:07.300 --> 00:05:07.900
Maestro Yue.

00:05:18.410 --> 00:05:18.990
Yun.

00:05:39.340 --> 00:05:40.230
Puedes irte.

00:06:05.700 --> 00:06:07.220
Shangguan Qian.

00:06:09.500 --> 00:06:10.370
